<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>nigga.my.id - Archive Node</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #111 0%, #1e1a17 50%, #2a1f1a 100%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
      color: #f1f1f1;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      padding: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      color: #ff5050;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-style: italic;
      color: transparent;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #888 0%, #888 25%, #cc3322 50%, #888 75%, #888 100%);
      background-size: 400% 100%;
      background-position: 100% 0;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      animation: warning-sweep 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes warning-sweep {
      0%   { background-position: 200% 0; }
      50%  { background-position: 0% 0; }
      100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .elsewhere {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #555;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .elsewhere a {
      color: transparent;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #555 0%, #555 25%, #c0bdb8 45%, #e8e4de 50%, #c0bdb8 55%, #555 75%, #555 100%);
      background-size: 400% 100%;
      background-position: 100% 0;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      text-decoration: none;
      animation: shimmer 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes shimmer {
      0%   { background-position: 200% 0; }
      50%  { background-position: 0% 0; }
      100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>nigga.my.id</h1>
  <p>This domain was originally intended for a small, private Minecraft server — a chaotic but exciting plan full of mods, cracked configs, and daydreams that fizzled out before the first block was placed.</p>

  <p>Unfortunately, <span class="highlight">the domain name triggered Minecraft's internal filter</span> — no matter how genuine the context, the launcher wouldn't allow it.</p>

  <p>So here it is now: untouched, unused — but still mine. Not a slur, not hate, just a relic from a quirky chapter that never went live.</p>

  <p>Whether you're here by mistake or on purpose: welcome. This is a landing page for a domain that couldn't quite spawn into the world it was meant to.</p>

  <div class="footer">
    &copy; 2025&ndash;<span id="year"></span> <a href="https://xiaocia.my.id">MAFY</a>
    <div class="elsewhere">the author can be found <a href="https://xiaocia.my.id">elsewhere</a>.</div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
